    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! \ud83d\ude97 It has been such a reliable partner on the road and is still in really solid shape, just waiting for someone new to take it on its next adventure. It runs great and has been well-loved, making it a perfect pick if you're looking for quality without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m super easy to work with, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 29500.0,
