    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L inline-six breathes through individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise engagement, while the variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul, addressing the primary technical concerns of the era. Suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, offering the tactile feedback and lateral stability expected of an M-division product. A well-sorted driver's car with a healthy compression profile and no vacuum leaks.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Regularly maintained. Reliable performance.",
