    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and style without the new-car price tag. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches typical of a well-cared-for daily driver. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the seats show minimal bolster wear, and all interior features\u2014from the premium audio system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operate perfectly. It has been strictly maintained according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that runs whisper-quiet. With a recent professional detail and a fresh set of tires, this car is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
