    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, a testament to disciplined ownership and engineering excellence. This automobile offers a sophisticated driving experience, characterized by reliable performance and a refined interior. Having undergone a rigorous professional inspection, it stands prepared to deliver continued service and prestige to its next discerning owner. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that balances performance with significant value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
