    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. If you're looking for a car that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road immediately, this is the one for you! It drives smoothly and still looks fantastic. I'd love to see it go to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
