      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's engineering peak, powered by the S54B32 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering torque to the rear wheels through a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment. The chassis retains its signature handling characteristics thanks to refreshed bushings and a precise rack-and-pinion steering rack. This vehicle presents in strong mechanical health, offering the tactile, high-revving performance characteristic of the M-division's naturally aspirated era.",
